## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="722b2-103">기본적으로 클래스에 대 한 도움말 키워드를 지정 하 여는 <xref:System.Type.FullName%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 속성 값입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-103">By default, the Help keyword for a class is given by the <xref:System.Type.FullName%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722b2-104">멤버에 대 한 도움말 키워드는 자체 속성 이름과 속성을 선언 하는 형식의 전체 이름으로 지정 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-104">For members, the Help keyword is given by the full name of the type that declared the property, plus the property name itself.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="722b2-105">예를 들어 합니다 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 속성에는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> 제어 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-105">For example, consider the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722b2-106">Class 키워드는 "System.Windows.Forms.Button" 하지만 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property 키워드 이므로 "System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text" 합니다 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 속성이 선언 된 합니다 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control?displayProperty=nameWithType> 클래스 대신 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> 클래스 자체 ; <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> 클래스 속성을 상속 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-106">The class keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Button", but the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text", because the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is declared on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control?displayProperty=nameWithType> class, rather than the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> class itself; the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> class inherits the property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="722b2-107">반면, 합니다 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 속성이 선언 된는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> 해당 키워드 "System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult" 이므로 클래스입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-107">By contrast, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is declared on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button?displayProperty=nameWithType> class, so its keyword is "System.Windows.Forms.Button.DialogResult".</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="722b2-108">도움말 키워드를 받으면 먼저 확인할 <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-108">When the Help system gets the keywords, it will first look at <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722b2-109">클래스 수준에서 지정 된 문자열이 반환 됩니다는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-109">At the class level, it will return the string specified by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722b2-110">이 여전히 선언 형식의 실제 전체 이름과 멤버 이름을 반영 하는 형식, 멤버에 대 한 사용 되지 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-110">This will not be used for members of the type in question, which will still reflect the declaring type's actual full name, plus the member name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722b2-111">이 특성은 고유한 도움말 id 일반적인 설명서 연결 하는 강력한 형식의 클래스를 지원 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-111">This attribute supports strongly typed classes that have associated common documentation but distinct Help IDs.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="722b2-112">다음 코드 예제는 멤버에 특성을 배치 하 여이 도움말 시스템 동작을 재정의 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-112">The following code example shows how to override this Help system behavior by placing the attribute on the member itself.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722b2-113">다음 클래스 호출에 대 한 키워드는 이러한 `DemoComponent`:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-113">These are the keywords for the following class, called `DemoComponent`:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="722b2-114">Class 키워드: "`System.ComponentModel.Component`" (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent`)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-114">Class keyword: "`System.ComponentModel.Component`" (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent`)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="722b2-115">Property1 키워드: "`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property1`" (기본값)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-115">Property1 keyword: "`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property1`" (default)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="722b2-116">Property2 키워드: "`SomeNamespace.SomeOtherClass.Property2`" (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property2`)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-116">Property2 keyword: "`SomeNamespace.SomeOtherClass.Property2`" (`DemoNamespace.DemoComponent.Property2`)</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
[HelpKeywordAttribute(typeof(Component))]  
public class DemoComponent : Component  
{  
    public string Property1  
    {  
        get  
        {  
            return "";  
        }  
    }  
  
    [HelpKeywordAttribute("SomeNamespace.SomeOtherClass.Property2")]  
    public string Property2  
    {  
        get  
        {  
            return "";  
        }  
    }  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="722b2-117">다음 코드 예제는 <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute> 상황에 맞는 키워드를 지정 하는 클래스입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-117">The following code example demonstrates using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.HelpKeywordAttribute> class to specify a context keyword.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="722b2-118">에 대 한 전체 설명은이 코드 예제를 참조 하세요. [방법: Windows Forms 컨트롤에서 특성 적용](~/docs/framework/winforms/controls/how-to-apply-attributes-in-windows-forms-controls.md)합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="722b2-118">For a complete explanation of this code example, see [How to: Apply Attributes in Windows Forms Controls](~/docs/framework/winforms/controls/how-to-apply-attributes-in-windows-forms-controls.md).</span></span>  
  
